content.rendered:
Directed by Rohit Jugraj.

Written by Ritesh Shah.

Cast Diljit Dosanjh(Arjun Patiala). Kriti Sanon(Ritu Randhawa). Varun Sharma(Onida Singh). Ronit Roy(Amarjeet Singh Gill). Seema Pahwa(Prapti Makkad (as Seema Bhargava)). Mohd. Zeeshan Ayyub(Sakool (as Mohammed Zeeshan Ayyub)). Amit Mehra(Baldev Rana). Nirmal Rishi(Arjun’s mother). Sunny Leone(Baby Narula) . Abhiruchi(Faryadi / Punjabi Aunty). Santosh Anand(PA to Producer). Ankit(Ahatha Gangster 1). Abhishek Banerjee(Director). Bharat Bhatia(Sukhi Bajwa). Alorika Chatterjee(Editor’s Mom). Mithilesh Chaturvedi(Bhatia ji). Gurmeet Chawla(Old Uncle & Jailor).Sudhir Dhara. Yash Diliprane(Market Boy). Abhishek Gaikwad(Clothing Shop Owner). Suhani Gandhi(Cameo). Subhasish Ghosh(Bad Guy 1 (as Shubahshish Ghosh)). Nikita Grover(Nikki Ahuja). Sumit Gulati(Anda). Neelam Gupta(Onida Mother). Gurleen(Paaji). Akshay Joshi(Kala Jamun). Chiya Joshi(Maid 1 (as Chiya Sharma)). Abhimanue Kamboj(Billu (as Abhimanue)). Vishwas Kapoor(Chief Guest / Judo Announcer). Vijay Kaushal(Dangal Announcer).Tareeq Ahmed Khan. Tarik Khan(Sharabi). Kisha(Onida Sister1). Himanshu Kohli(Dlibaugh Singh). Ankush Kulshreshtha(Kundan). Rishi Kulshreshtha(Onida Mama). Haripriya Lodhia(Onida Sister3). Mursalin(Afeemchi). Pyarali Narayan(Market Father).

Languages Hindi. Punjabi.

Producers Karan Gill. Kushagra Kulshrestha. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Sandeep Leyzell. Ashok Shetty. Dinesh Vijan.

Production Bake My Cake Films. Maddock Films. T-Series Films.
